<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要把你挤扁！” 食人魔大吼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23616</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用手紧紧地握着普斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23616</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 普斯大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快停下！要不然你就不能拿到钱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33158</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔不再挤了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么意思？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯转了转眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42874</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你把我挤扁，我就不能付钱给你了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔想了想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在就把你放下。” 食人魔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不会又逃跑吧？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62296</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯把爪子放在胸前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69991</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然不跑了。你可以相信我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔把普斯放在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才骗了你，对不起。” 普斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我之前并不相信你可以把自己变大。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86912</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那你现在知道我可以了吧。” 食人魔骄傲地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93155</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以做很多奇妙的事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……” 普斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那……你可以把自己变小吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然可以！” 食人魔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯怀疑地看着食人魔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120023</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125820</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不相信？” 食人魔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125820</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯耸耸肩。“不太相信。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔生气了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔开始变小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143826</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151240</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，他就变成了一只老鼠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普斯咧嘴笑了。他一下子扑了过去！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166457</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！” 食人魔大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！” 咕噜！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
